Putera Zhennan.

736
00:38:42,840 --> 00:38:44,570
Mengikut adat resam kita,

737
00:38:44,670 --> 00:38:45,850
anda mesti

738
00:38:45,880 --> 00:38:47,070
tinggal di kediaman berasingan

739
00:38:47,070 --> 00:38:48,590
sebelum majlis perkahwinan.

740
